{"id":20275,"date":"2024-01-24T14:51:58","date_gmt":"2021-03-24T09:21:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=20275"},"modified":"2022-05-30T15:58:41","modified_gmt":"2022-05-30T10:28:41","slug":"colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/","title":{"rendered":"6 Colour Combination For Bedroom According To Vastu And The Changes They Attract"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>The dominant colours in your bedroom influence your mood more than you think<\/em>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever enter a room and immediately feel your mood elevate or fall? Some rooms feel claustrophobic, while some fill you with joy. The colours in a room do more to affect our moods than we give them credit for. The age-old wisdom of Vastu Shastra has long spoken about the vibrations of colours and their influence on our attitudes and behaviour. Whether you\u2019re moving into a new home or feel like redoing your current room, choosing the colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu is a good idea.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can pick the best colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu based on the end goal you\u2019d like to achieve. According to Vastu Shashtra, different colours\u2019 vibrations boost or mellow a range of emotions and feelings. Based on one\u2019s personality, the recommendations also direct you to or against specific colours. Short-tempered people should stay away from red-dominant rooms, while people prone to laziness shouldn\u2019t be around shades of blue for too long.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With details on the positive changes colours can attract into your life, here\u2019s a guide to help you pick a colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Purple As Part Of The Colour Combination For Bedroom According To Vastu<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Feel like your life has been on a downer for some time? Filling your room with the healing properties of purple will do you a world of good. According to Vastu Shashtra, the rich colour is said to represent wealth, luxury and poise. It\u2019s no wonder then that so many royal courts in India featured upholstery in intense shades of purple.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The energy of purple is believed to inspire feelings of richness and royalty. This colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu is particularly recommended for those with an inferiority complex. Purple helps one develop feelings of self-respect, courage and graciousness.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142153\/royal-purple-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Purple is the perfect colour combination for bedroom according to vastu perfect choice for an extravagant headboard \" data-id=\"20281\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142153\/royal-purple-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/attachment\/royal-purple-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/\" class=\"wp-image-20281\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142153\/royal-purple-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142153\/royal-purple-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142153\/royal-purple-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142153\/royal-purple-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Royal purple is the perfect choice for an extravagant headboard that touches the ceiling<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Violet In Colour Combination For Bedroom According To Vastu Invites Confidence And Contentment<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Life can get overwhelming for the best of us, but it often feels like a neverending burden for some people. No matter what they do, they feel like it\u2019s not enough. You may need a little violet in your room if you tend to feel unhappy with life, no matter what the circumstances are. It\u2019s also a good colour combination for the master bedroom according to Vastu for those who find it difficult to make a decision.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The energies of violet are pretty influential and said to trigger contentment feelings for a room\u2019s inhabitants. The colour represents satisfaction, confidence and mental peace. It also helps one develop a decisive state of mind and enhances your spiritual side.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142209\/violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Violet is the best colour combination for master bedroom according to vastu which truly stands out against a plain white wall\" data-id=\"20283\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142209\/violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/attachment\/violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/\" class=\"wp-image-20283\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142209\/violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142209\/violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142209\/violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142209\/violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A sleek violet headboard in a glossy finish truly stands out against a plain white wall<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Yellow In Colour Combination For Bedroom According To Vastu Is A Ray Of Sunshine For Everyone<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>No prizes for guessing that sunshiney yellow represents all things happiness and joy. Life\u2019s daily routine can wear one out, but if you feel like you\u2019ve been low on energy more than usual, you need yellow energy to cheer you up and buzzing like a bee again. This bright colour boosts positive feelings and optimism.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It\u2019s also a good colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu for individuals with a lazy personality. Like the morning sunlight kicking weariness out, yellow motivates one into a state of activity and achievement. The colour is also recommended for small rooms. Its broadening effect makes a compact room look more spacious.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142232\/yellow-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Yellow in colour combination for bedroom according to vastu with splash yellow on one entire wall of your bedroom\" data-id=\"20286\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142232\/yellow-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/attachment\/yellow-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/\" class=\"wp-image-20286\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142232\/yellow-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142232\/yellow-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142232\/yellow-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142232\/yellow-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Splash yellow on one entire wall of your bedroom to make it look bigger<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Yellow And Violet In Colour Combination For Bedroom According To Vastu Help Prepare You For Important Exams<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides happiness and positivity, the illuminating qualities of yellow also represent intelligence and intellect. According to Vastu Shashtra, the colour yellow in a room is said to enhance the occupant\u2019s mental abilities. Therefore, this colour is highly recommended for the bedrooms of school going children or individuals pursuing studies or intellectual activities of any kind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you find it difficult to concentrate or if you&#8217;re the kind who loses focus quickly, introduce yellow into your room as it has a stabilising effect on the mind. Violet is another colour that represents knowledge and concentration. So, yellow and violet is the best colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu if you\u2019re preparing for important exams.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142224\/yellow-and-violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Yellow and violet in colour combination for bedroom according to vastu with touches of yellow and violet in the room\u2019s furnishings\" data-id=\"20285\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142224\/yellow-and-violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/attachment\/yellow-and-violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/\" class=\"wp-image-20285\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142224\/yellow-and-violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142224\/yellow-and-violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142224\/yellow-and-violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142224\/yellow-and-violet-in-colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Instead of big changes, introduce touches of yellow and violet in the room\u2019s furnishings<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Violet In Colour Combination For Bedroom According To Vastu Improves Memory And Focus<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Violet shares many properties with yellow. Like the sunshine shade, this deeper colour also represents knowledge. While yellow boosts one\u2019s mental abilities, violet improves your memory and concentration by bringing stability to your mind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A violet colour palette is the best colour combination for the bedroom according to Vastu for those involved in knowledge-based, intellectual or mental activities for the majority of their day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142201\/violet-colour-palette-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"Violet in colour combination for bedroom according to vastu with a patterned wallpaper\" data-id=\"20282\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142201\/violet-colour-palette-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.