rsonalities without having any adverse effects. However, the wisdom of Vastu Shashtra cautions against painting your entire house white. This is believed to turn occupants egoistic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142217\/white-colour-combination-for-bedroom-walls-as-per-vastu.jpg\" alt=\"White is the best colour combination for bedroom walls according to vastu with a personalised gallery\" data-id=\"20284\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142217\/white-colour-combination-for-bedroom-walls-as-per-vastu.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/colour-combination-for-bedroom-according-to-vastu\/attachment\/white-colour-combination-for-bedroom-walls-as-per-vastu\/\" class=\"wp-image-20284\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142217\/white-colour-combination-for-bedroom-walls-as-per-vastu.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142217\/white-colour-combination-for-bedroom-walls-as-per-vastu-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142217\/white-colour-combination-for-bedroom-walls-as-per-vastu-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/24142217\/white-colour-combination-for-bedroom-walls-as-per-vastu-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A personalised gallery is the best way to bring white walls to life<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what properties the different colours represent, identify your life condition and the changes you would like to introduce. It then gets easier to decide the colour combination for bedroom according to Vastu. You don\u2019t always need to redo your entire room or paint the walls to make your bedroom compatible with Vastu Shashtra. You can simply introduce various decor elements or furnishing in the Vastu colour combination to achieve your goals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Also Read:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about colour combination for bedroom according to vastu, also explore <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/wall-colour-combination-for-small-bedroom\/\">Wall Colour Combination For Small Bedroom<\/a>.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designca